com.esri.mo2.ui.lyt
Class ElementSelection

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.ui.lyt.ElementSelection
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClipboardOwner, Transferable
public class ElementSelection
extends Object
implements Transferable, ClipboardOwner

This class provide functionality similar to the StringSelection class in JDK. It is used for transferring an Element by using system clipboard and supports two data flavors, Elements and java.util.LinkList for layout elements.
